a7-4590-bf8d-f9df06162d4d\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"warning\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-11T05:19:24.96415072Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["frontend-0", "frontend-2", "frontend-1", "adservice-0", "adservice-2", "adservice-1"], "service_name": ["frontend", "adservice"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-03", "aiops-k8s-04", "aiops-k8s-07", "aiops-k8s-08"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault occurred from 2025-06-11T05:10:35Z to 2025-06-11T05:21:35Z. Please identify the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-11 05:10:35+00:00 to 2025-06-11 05:21:35+00:00"}, "trace_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的链路追踪数据，我对故障进行了详细分析。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"error_ratio\", \"frontend->adservice\", \"checkoutservice->cartservice\", \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\", \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\", \"checkoutservice->emailservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"AdService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"AdService调用延迟从正常5.5秒激增至497秒（约90倍增长），出现大量context deadline exceeded错误（946次）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"PaymentService\", \n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"PaymentService/Charge操作延迟从12.8秒增至53.5秒（约4.2倍增长）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CartService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"CartService/AddItem操作延迟从3.9秒增至25.5秒（约6.6倍增长），EmptyCart操作延迟从2.3秒增至13.8秒（约6倍增长）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ShippingService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"ShippingService相关操作延迟普遍增加，GetQuote从185ms增至768ms，ShipOrder从14.4秒增至41.3秒\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现：**\n\n1. **AdService是主要根因**：三个frontend实例对AdService的GetAds调用都出现严重延迟（90倍增长），并伴随大量超时错误，表明AdService完全不可用或严重过载。\n\n2. **CheckoutService受影响严重**：作为核心业务流程，CheckoutService调用的多个下游服务都出现延迟，包括PaymentService、CartService、ShippingService和EmailService。\n\n3. **错误传播路径**：AdService故障 → Frontend服务受影响 → CheckoutService流程受阻 → 整个订单处理链路异常。\n\n4. **网络层面问题**：存在RST_STREAM错误码，可能涉及gRPC连接问题或网络中断。\n\n建议优先排查AdService的健康状态和资源使用情况，同时检查网络连接稳定性。", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的指标数据，我现在进行故障分析。从数据中我观察到多个服务出现了响应时间异常，特别是frontend服务的响应时间显著增加。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"rrt\", \"rrt_max\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\", \"pod_processes\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt和rrt_max指标显著异常，响应时间从正常中位数12084.98ms飙升至故障期36509.29ms，增长205%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0的rrt中位数从12084.98ms升至36509.29ms(变化率100.52%)，rrt_max从257931ms升至619148ms(变化率82.37%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-1\", \n      \"reason\": \"rrt和rrt_max指标严重恶化，响应时间从12322.19ms上升至36044.05ms\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-1的rrt中位数从12322.19ms升至36044.05ms(变化率98.09%)，rrt_max从285799ms升至620796ms(变化率73.9%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt和rrt_max指标异常，响应时间性能严重下降\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-2的rrt中位数从12412.66ms升至36570.98ms(变化率98.64%)，rrt_max从281409ms升至614710ms(变化率74.39%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max的P99值异常飙升，从4146.3ms升至68735ms，增长1672%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"paymentservice-1的rrt_max P99值从4146.3ms飙升至68735ms(变化率1577.24%)，表明存在严重的性能问题\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"emailservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max的P99值显著增加，从7610.08ms升至61912.9ms\",\n      \"evidence\": \"emailservice-1的rrt_max P99值从7610.08ms升至61912.9ms(变化率713.92%)，表明该服务响应时间极度不稳定\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "log_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的日志数据，我已经完成了分析。以下是详细的分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"DeadlineExceeded\", \"context deadline exceeded\", \"RST_STREAM\", \"CANCEL\", \"Byteman agent\", \"InvocationTargetException\", \"Agent failed to start\", \"adservice--latency\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"adservice 服务出现 Byteman agent 启动失败和延迟注入问题，导致服务响应超时和连接被取消\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Agent failed to start!, Caused by: java.lang.Exception: Main : attempting to load Byteman agent more than once, AdService-getRandomAds-latency-1749618636 execute()\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"frontend 服务调用 adservice 时出现大量 DeadlineExceeded 错误和 RST_STREAM 连接取消\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to get ads: rpc error: code = DeadlineExceeded desc = context deadline exceeded, stream terminated by RST_STREAM with error code: CANCEL\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析总结**：\n\n1. **主要错误模式**：\n   - 大量 `DeadlineExceeded` 和 `context deadline exceeded` 错误\n   - `RST_STREAM` 连接被取消错误\n   - Byteman agent 启动失败和重复加载异常\n\n2. **故障链分析**：\n   - **根因**: adservice 服务的 Byteman agent 出现故障（启动失败、重复加载）\n   - **影响**: 导致 adservice 响应延迟，无法正常提供服务\n   - **表现**: frontend 调用 adservice 时出现超时和连接取消错误\n\n3. **关键证据**：\n   - adservice 出现 `Agent failed to start!` 和 Byteman agent 相关异常\n   - frontend 大量报错显示无法获取广告服务，错误类型为超时和连接取消\n   - 故障时间窗口与用户提供的异常时间段完全吻合"}
